title: Full Show (Cowboys get first win, Brady beats Saints, Trey Lance out for season)
description:
00:00 Cowboys beat the Bengals 20-17. Will Rush and Parsons keep the Cowboys afloat until Dak returns?
24:28 Brady and the Bucs finally beat the Saints 20-10. Did the Evans and Lattimore fight ignite the Buccaneers to a victory?
53:41 Cowboys beat the Bengals on a last second field goal. Will Dallas be okay this season?
1:07:57 Panthers lose to the Giants 19-16. Are there any bright spots for Baker and the 0-2 Panthers?
1:22:37 Tua throws for 6 TDs in a 42-38 comeback win against the Ravens. Stunned by the Dolphins 21-point comeback?
1:32:08 Brady and the Bucs snap skid against the Saints. How impressive has Brady been this season?
1:41:59 Trey Lance suffered a fractured ankle in win over the Seahawks. How will the 49ers handle the return of Jimmy G as their starting QB?
1:47:48 Mike Evans and Marshon Lattimore are ejected for their fight.
1:54:28 Cousins and the Vikings face off against Hurts and the Eagles on MNF. Who will move on to 2-0?
